  "description": "Information you thought was hidden becomes common knowledge, diminishing your advantage.",
  "content": "The secret you'd been carefully guarding—or strategically holding—is suddenly no secret at all. Someone else revealed it, or circumstances exposed it, or it simply became too obvious to hide. The knowledge that gave you an edge, that made you valuable or powerful or dangerous, is now just... common information. Everyone knows now. The asymmetry of knowledge that you'd been navigating has shifted, and not in your favor.",
